- RegExp. (Regular Expressions):
--------------------------------
used to search or validate a text

1- Pattern: let re = /hello/

2- Modifier:
	- i: case-insensitive matching.
	- ^: begining with 
	- $: end with
	- .: matches ONE character
	- *:
	- ?: optional character
	- \: Escape character


syntax: /pattern/modifiers;

functions:
------------
.exec() return result in an array or null.


